{"header":{"word":"פַּ֫חַד","entry":7627,"letter":"פ","strongs":6343,"page":808},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" I. [[פַּ֫חַד]]:49 ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.m.","body":":1811,7 dread;&#8212;&#180;[[פ]] abs. Ge 31:42 +, cstr. 1Sa 11:7 +, sf. [[פַּחְדְְּ]] De 2:25, Ps 119:120, [[פַּחְדּוֹ]] Job 13:11, 1Ch 14:17, etc.; pl. [[פְּחָדִים]] Job 15:21:&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" dread, &#180;[[י]]&#180;[[פ]], i.e. before &#180;[[י]], oft. (not alw.) terrifying, unfitting for action, &#134; Is 2:10, Is 2:19, Is 2:21, 1Sa 11:7, 2Ch 14:13, 2Ch 17:10, so [[אֱהִֽים]] &#180;[[פ]] &#134; 20:29, c. sf. Job 13:11, Ps 119:120 trembleth for dread of thee; c. genit. obj. Isr., &#134; De 2:25 (&#8214;[[יִרְאָה]]), De 11:25 (&#8214;[[מוֹרָא]]), Ps 105:38, Es 8:17, Es 9:2, [[אוֹיֵב]] &#180;[[פ]] &#134; Ps 64:2, of individual &#134; 1Ch 14:17, Es 9:3; c. genit. obj. rei Pr 1:33; abs., in gen., Ex 15:16 (song; &#8214;[[אֵימָ֫תָה]]), Job 4:14 (&#8214;[[רְעָדָה]]), Je 30:5 (&#8214;[[קוֹל]] [[חֲרָדָה]]) +; as acc. cogn. c. [[פָּחַד]] Ps 14:5 + (v. [[פָּחַד]]); c. genit. subj. &#134; Pr 1:26, Pr 1:27 (both &#8214;[[אֵיד]]) De 28:67. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" = object of dread &#134; Ps 31:12, Ps 36:2, [[אֵלַי]] &#180;[[פ]] Job 31:23; [[פַּחַד פָּחַדְתִּי]] &#134; Job 3:25; [[מִקּוֹל הַפַּחַד]] &#134; Is 24:18 sound of the disaster, for &#180;[[מִפְּנֵי הַפּ]] of orig. Je 48:44, but [[קוֹל פְּחָדִים]] &#134; Job 15:21 = a sound of terrors; &#180;[[פ]] [[פִּתְאׂם]] Job 22:10, Pr 3:25. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"3.","body":" as design. dei &#134; [[יִחְחָק]] &#180;[[פ]] Ge 31:42 (&#8214;[[אֱהֵֽי אַבְרָהָם]]), so v:Ge 31:53 (&#8214; id.; both E).\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}